We have derived the actual cost of construction as per books of accounts in the following manner;
Where
Cost of Construction of which Invoices are received (A)-25,92,20,467
Unbilled Advances i.e Cost incurred and paid but bills not received for the same(B)-1,17,11,239
Sundry Creditors ( C)-4,07,35,260
Hence the acutal cost of construction should be Rs. 270931706 (A) +(B)
However, the Form-3 requires us to report Cost of Construction incurred & paid i.e. (A)+ (B) - (C ) which amounts to Rs. 23,01,96,446
